### Vehicle Message Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = your_auth_token_here

### Get all message templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get traffic templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/traffic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get maintenance templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get safety templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/safety
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get administrative templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/administrative
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get operational templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/operational
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get communication templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/templates/communication
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a vehicle message using a template
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "1",
  "sentByUserId": "1",
  "message": "Heavy traffic detected ahead. Estimated delay: 15 minutes. Maintain safe distance.",
  "severity": "WARNING"
}

### Create a critical message
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "2",
  "sentByUserId": "1",
  "message": "EMERGENCY: Stop the vehicle immediately and contact dispatch.",
  "severity": "CRITICAL"
}

### Get all vehicle messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get vehicle messages with severity filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages?severity=CRITICAL&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get messages for specific vehicle
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/vehicle/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get specific message by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a message
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Updated message content",
  "severity": "NORMAL"
}

### Delete a message
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/vehicle-messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

